A serene realistic lakeside scene stretches before the eye, filled with natural beauty and peaceful detail. The calm lake glistens under the soft golden glow of the sun, its surface rippling gently with the breeze, reflecting the sky in shades of blue and silver. Along the water’s edge, tall green grasses and reeds sway lightly, while wildflowers bloom in splashes of yellow, purple, and white, adding a gentle vibrancy to the shoreline. Smooth stones and weathered driftwood rest naturally at the banks, blending with the earth tones of the soil. Towering trees with dense green foliage line the lakeside, their reflections shimmering softly in the water, while distant rolling hills rise in muted layers of green and blue. A small wooden pier stretches out into the lake, worn yet sturdy, with a lone rowboat tied quietly to its side, rocking slightly with the water’s motion. The atmosphere is calm and meditative, the scene alive with subtle details—the sound of water lapping, the rustle of leaves, the faint call of birds echoing across the horizon. Captured in a wide cinematic still image with a straight-on perspective, the scene emphasizes the realism of light, texture, and reflection, immersing the viewer in tranquil natural beauty. cinematic still image, ultra-detailed, hyper-realistic landscape, soft dramatic lighting.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: On the tranquil shore of a serene lake, a breathtakingly realistic scene unfolds, where the natural beauty of the landscape takes center stage and, within it, a small figure of child Krishna adds divine innocence. The lake stretches wide and calm, its shimmering surface reflecting the golden glow of the sun and the soft blues of the sky, while gentle ripples dance across the water. Along the bank, tall grasses sway, wildflowers bloom in vibrant yellows and purples, and smooth stones line the edge where the earth meets the water. Towering trees frame the background, their leafy crowns mirrored in the lake’s surface, while distant hills fade softly into the horizon. At the edge of the shore, appearing small within the vast scenery, child Krishna plays joyfully—his tiny form glowing with smooth blue skin, curly black hair crowned by a delicate peacock feather, and a simple yellow dhoti tied with a golden waistband. His small hands splash gently at the water’s edge, his laughter radiating innocence, his anklets chiming faintly as his bare feet press into the soft earth. A subtle golden aura surrounds him, making him a divine jewel within the expansive landscape. Captured in a wide cinematic still image, the camera frames the grand lakeside scenery with Krishna placed small in the composition, emphasizing both the vastness of nature and the tender, playful presence of the divine child. cinematic still image, aidmaimageupgrader, ultra-detailed, hyper-realistic landscape with divine child portrait, soft dramatic lighting.
